{"data":[{"date":"09:09 12/07","title":"\"\u0110T Anh v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dt-anh-van-thieu-mot-manh-ghep-de-thanh-cong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Chris Waddle c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh BBC cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.</h2><h2>\u0110T Anh thua \u0111\u1eafng Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTam S\u01b0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi Kieran Trippier c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng d\u1eady v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ivan Perisic g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a trong hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Mandzukic s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Pickford \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Balkan.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/DT-Anh-that-bai-vi-thieu-mot-cau-thu-sang-tao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110T\u00a0Anh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Southgate \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Nga. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Chris Waddle c\u1ee7a k\u00eanh BBC Sport cho r\u1eb1ng Tam S\u01b0 c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Euro 2020.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ed9 ba trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 khi \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPickford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Jordan Henderson c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc v\u1ec1 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Dele Alli b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i im ti\u1ebfng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. Raheem Sterling th\u00ec v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi. B\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-gay-soc-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190989.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1175","checkdouble":"191014"},{"date":"09:31 12/07","title":"\u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/dt-anh-thua-croatia-vi-phai-mac-ao-dau-mau-trang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, thay v\u00ec m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf may m\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f9ng Tam S\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1966.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br />\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh thua v\u00ec \u00e1o tr\u1eafng?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Guardian t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1950, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0u \u00e1o c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t l\u1edbn. Khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, Tam S\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 cho r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh vao ban ket World Cup 2018 day thuyet phuc.\" title=\"\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Fabio-Capello-phat-bieu-ve-Jordan-Pickford-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Anh th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 ba tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi m\u1eb7c s\u1eafc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nT\u1eeb n\u0103m 1950, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Euro v\u00e0 World Cup v\u1edbi 71 l\u1ea7n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, 24 tr\u1eadn m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. T\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng gi\u1eefa hai m\u00e0u \u00e1o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh l\u00e0 46% (11 tr\u1eadn) so v\u1edbi 39% khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng (28 tr\u1eadn). Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1996 c\u0169ng v\u1edbi s\u1eafc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. T\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 thua khi \u0110T Anh m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi 17% (4 tr\u1eadn), so v\u1edbi 39% khi m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng (28 tr\u1eadn).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u00e1o tr\u1eafng, 3 l\u1ea7n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, \u0110T Anh to\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, Colombia v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Tunisia, hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Tam S\u01b0 c\u00f2n ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia v\u1edbi s\u1eafc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n ba tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng, \u0110T Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9. Hai tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Tam S\u01b0 thua B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Croatia - th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea5c m\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 tan v\u1ee1.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec sao \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o tr\u1eafng?<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ph\u00e2n chia nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u, \u0110T Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eb7c \u00e1o &quot;ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0&quot; khi g\u1eb7p Anh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0u \u00e1o &quot;ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0&quot; c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 caro \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng, s\u1eafc \u00e1o n\u00e0y tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 (tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecf).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Anh thua Croatia vi phai mac ao dau mau trang?\" title=\"\u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng?\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/dt-anh-thua-croatia-vi-phai-mac-ao-dau-mau-trang.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Anh thua Croatia v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0110T Croatia m\u1eb7c \u00e1o t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u khi g\u1eb7p Anh. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu thua 1-2 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-van-thieu-mot-manh-ghep-de-thanh-cong-469-191014.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ha-guc-anh-cau-thu-croatia-pose-anh-an-mung-465-191012.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Croatia thi nhau pose \u1ea3nh \u0103n m\u1eebng l\u00ean MXH</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mourinho-noi-ve-that-bai-tran-anh-vs-croatia-421-191011.html\">Mourinho an \u1ee7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau khi tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay-421-191010.html\">Sao Croatia: T\u01b0\u1edfng Anh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn v\u1eady!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-bao-ve-kane-sau-man-tang-hinh-truoc-croatia-469-191009.html\">HLV Southgate b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Kane sau m\u00e0n t\u00e0ng h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/mario-mandzukic-goi-chien-thang-cua-dt-croatia-la-phep-mau-465-191008.html\">Mario Mandzukic g\u1ecdi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0 ph\u00e9p m\u00e0u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N.D (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1174","checkdouble":"191015"},{"date":"09:30 12/07","title":"Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1eabng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/barca-muon-mua-hazard-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CalcioMercato ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus hy sinh Higuain</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o giao k\u00e8o g\u1eafn b\u00f3 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Gonzalo Higuain kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 trung phong s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 d\u1ecbch chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh sang m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CR7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/ronaldo-toi-juventus-muon-ban-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 chuy\u00ean trang chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Calciomercato.com c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ecf ra chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi Juventus \u0111ang th\u1eeba th\u00e3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat gi\u1ecfi th\u00ec Chelsea l\u1ea1i \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Alvaro Morata h\u01a1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Chelsea d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh mua v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Higuain n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus muon doi Higuain lay Morata\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n thay th\u1ebf Morata b\u1eb1ng Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn tin Higuain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Juventus thanh l\u00fd trong c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin m\u1eebng v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o The Blues b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t ai l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Antonio Conte hay b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Chelsea tin HLV m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Higuain. Conte hay Sarri \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Serie A. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Juventus s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 55 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-juventus-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-190942.html\">Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo-176-190965.html\">S\u1ebfp Juventus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus-180-190910.html\">&ldquo;Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1173","checkdouble":"191016"},{"date":"10:32 12/07","title":"\u0110\u00f2i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p, \u0110T Anh b\u1ecb Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/doi-vao-chung-ket-gap-phap-dt-anh-bi-mbappe-cuoi-vao-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Croatia r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh v\u00ec th\u00f3i \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng.\r\n</h2><h2>Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t C\u0110V Tam S\u01b0<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111em chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau 52 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Anh qu\u1ed1c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1. H\u1ecd g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Croatia c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. Sau th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin m\u1eebng, khi \u0110T s\u1ecdc ca-ro \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng l\u1ef1c ki\u1ec7t, ch\u1ec9 trong 10 ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7 t\u1edbi C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Instagram, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh &ldquo;It&rsquo;s Coming Home &ndash; B\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi&rdquo;, c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef: &ldquo;T\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i, t\u00f4i y\u00eau n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Nh\u01b0ng g\u1eedi t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u0103ng m\u1ea1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng m\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mbap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u1ea1o \u0110T Anh v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba qua, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eedi r\u1ee7a Kylian Mbappe v\u00ec th\u00f3i c\u00e2u gi\u1edd, \u0103n v\u1ea1. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a PSG c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng v\u1eeba, khi \u0111em kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec7u &ldquo;\u0111em b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng&rdquo; c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ra ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Les Bleus s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i World Cup, v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay-421-191010.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay-421-191010.html\">Sao Croatia: T\u01b0\u1edfng Anh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, h\u00f3a ra v\u1eabn v\u1eady!</span><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Sime Vrsaljko l\u00ean m\u1eb7t kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Tam S\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n nguy\u00ean h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn Croatia 2-1 Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-190993.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-gareth-southgate-noi-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-anh-465-190993.html\">HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 khi \u0110T Anh qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1172","checkdouble":"191017"},{"date":"10:20 12/07","title":"Eric Dier n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/eric-dier-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tuyen-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dier th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Croatia t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. G\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o \u0111em chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0 kh\u1ea9u hi\u1ec3u m\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V h\u00f4 h\u00e0o trong th\u1eddi gian di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham &ndash; Eric Dier t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb \u0111ang g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u00edt ra ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u00e0 c\u1ed5 v\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia\" title=\"Dier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/eric-dier-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tuyen-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf - ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n nhau h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Ph\u00e1p 2 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc (k\u1ef3 EURO 2016), khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 theo c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 n\u00ean th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i theo c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo; &ndash; Eric Dier chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Dier ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, d\u00f9 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Jordan Henderson thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7. Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y, \u0110T Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 v\u1edbi \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Football is NOT coming home!&rdquo; &ndash; Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb Croatia l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng. Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span><br>\r\nMarcus Rashford th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau khi Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1171","checkdouble":"191018"},{"date":"10:00 12/07","title":"Ronaldo t\u1edbi, ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Juventus chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i \u201ccu\u1ed1n g\u00f3i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ronaldo-toi-juventus-muon-ban-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CalcioMercato ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 n\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho Chelsea c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus hy sinh Higuain</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o giao k\u00e8o g\u1eafn b\u00f3 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Gonzalo Higuain kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 trung phong s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Juventus. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 d\u1ecbch chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh sang m\u1ed9t c\u00e2y s\u0103n b\u00e0n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ee3p l\u00fd khi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a CR7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 suy gi\u1ea3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/ronaldo-toi-juventus-muon-ban-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Gonzalo Higuain suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 chuy\u00ean trang chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Calciomercato.com c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Juventus mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ecf ra chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea m\u1eebng th\u1ea7m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi Juventus \u0111ang th\u1eeba th\u00e3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat gi\u1ecfi th\u00ec Chelsea l\u1ea1i \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Alvaro Morata h\u01a1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Real Madrid \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Chelsea d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh mua v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Higuain n\u1eb1m trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus muon doi Higuain lay Morata\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n thay th\u1ebf Morata b\u1eb1ng Higuain</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea l\u1ea1i nh\u1eadn tin Higuain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb Juventus thanh l\u00fd trong c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tin m\u1eebng v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o The Blues b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ed1t ai l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Chelsea v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Antonio Conte hay b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u Chelsea tin HLV m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Higuain. Conte hay Sarri \u0111\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Serie A. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Juventus s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0o b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ch\u1ecbu chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 55 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-juventus-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-172-190942.html\">Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo-176-190965.html\">S\u1ebfp Juventus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus-180-190910.html\">&ldquo;Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1170","checkdouble":"191019"},{"date":"10:52 12/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u1ea1n n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau khi \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/nguoi-anh-can-nuoc-mat-sau-khi-dt-quoc-gia-guc-nga-o-ban-ket.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f3c ng\u1ea5t khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2>Tam S\u01b0 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc, C\u0110V nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00ean m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 (It&rsquo;s Coming Home) t\u1eeb sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u1ecfi n\u00f3i c\u00e1c hooligan c\u1ee7a Anh k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai c\u1ee7a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia. Sau nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi \u0111\u1ee5ng ph\u1ea3i Croatia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Kieran Trippier, h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m ngh\u00ecn C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t cu\u1ed3ng v\u00ec vui m\u1eebng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i sau b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Ivan Perisic, r\u1ed3i chuy\u1ec3n sang t\u1eadn c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi Mario Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a th\u00e1ng B\u1ea3y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ea7y kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m, t\u1eeb c\u00e1c kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0i c\u1ee7a SV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00ea nh\u00e0. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh C\u0110V tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f3c ng\u1ea5t sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style