/world-cup-2018/rashford-khoc-het-nuoc-mat-sau-that-bai-cua-anh-truoc-croatia-421-190997.html\">Rashford kh\u00f3c h\u1ebft n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span><br>\r\nMarcus Rashford th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau khi Tam s\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-dt-croatia-lam-nen-lich-su-465-190995.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/14.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-dt-croatia-lam-nen-lich-su-465-190995.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Croatia t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed nh\u01b0 m\u1edf h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Luzhniki m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1edf Moscow, hay xa h\u01a1n \u1edf ch\u00ednh qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 khi \u0110T Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1169","checkdouble":"191020"},{"date":"11:38 12/07","title":"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 12/7: M.U ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Darmian cho Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/ngay-hom-nay-127.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a H\u00e8 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (12/7). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 t\u1eeb c\u00e1c CLB l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Darmian cho Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Matteo Darmian nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 canh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua Darmian \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Man Utd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Calcionews24 cho bi\u1ebft gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Fabio Paratici \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Darmian, Tullio Tinti \u1edf Milan, tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t. Man Utd ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 20 tri\u1ec7u euro, trong khi nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu chi ra c\u00f3 13 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Darmian v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, d\u00f9 anh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Italia thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngo\u00e0i Juventus, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Torino c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Napoli, Inter Milan theo \u0111u\u1ed5i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 127, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00f4m nay ng\u00e0y 127, tin n\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/inter-milan-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Darmian</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00f3n t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Arsenal v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p, FC Lorient. Guendouzi tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a PSG tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho H\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Lorient n\u0103m 2014. Th\u00e1ng 10/2016, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 17, Guendouzi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i 1 c\u1ee7a Lorient v\u00e0 ra s\u00e2n 30 tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 19 tu\u1ed5i, Arsenal ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 cho Lorient 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. T\u1ea1i Arsenal, Guendouzi s\u1ebd kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 29. Ngay trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft CLB, Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tham gia t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 sau Bernd Leno, Stephan Lichtsteiner, Sokratis Papastathopoulos v\u00e0 Lucas Torreira.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/210541-4221396001_5807910584001_5807900029001-vs.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Lucas Torreira, c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt gi\u1edd Arsenal ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Matteo Guendouzi t\u1eeb CLB...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli: &quot;Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea thay Conte&quot;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Antonio Conte trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi \u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Napoli. Tuy nhi\u00ean Chelsea g\u1eb7p ch\u00fat tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c v\u1ec1 ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng do Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Napoli \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 v\u1ebb m\u1ecdi kh\u00fac m\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u1ed5n tho\u1ea3. \u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch De Laurentiis c\u1ee7a Napoli cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Sarri trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. &quot;Sarri s\u1eafp s\u1eeda t\u1edbi Chelsea r\u1ed3i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. C\u00e1c lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd cho lu\u1eadt s\u01b0 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi Sarri s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho. \u00d4ng De Laurentiis cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi Man City v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u00e0o hai tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng Jorginho l\u1ea1i th\u00edch s\u1ed1ng \u1edf London h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Manchester n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Chelsea&quot;.</div>\r\n<h2>Nani CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Sporting Lisbon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a MU v\u1eeba ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 m\u00e0 anh t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 2005-2007 v\u00e0 2014-2015 (\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c MU \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n). Nani gia nh\u1eadp Sporting Lisbon l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"nani bo dao nha\" title=\"nani b\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e0o nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/9/2/nani-bo-dao-nha-dang-la-doi-bong-manh-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nani</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Yaya Toure \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c West Ham v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y c\u0169 m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi chia tay Man City, Yaya Toure \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c West Ham United t\u00edch c\u1ef1c s\u0103n \u0111\u00f3n. Theo t\u1edd Goals, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n London \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao 35 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0. N\u1ebfu gia nh\u1eadp &quot;The Hammers&quot;, c\u1eadu em nh\u00e0 Toure s\u1ebd c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Manuel Pellegrini khi HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB n\u00e0y m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1168","checkdouble":"191021"},{"date":"11:17 12/07","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: \u201cK\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t\u201d Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thay v\u00ec tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United, Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Jose Mourinho d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c <em>anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng, tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Madrid</em>. Trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m, anh \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb hu\u00fdt s\u00e1o v\u00e0 ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u b\u1edfi ch\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Real tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1eeb c\u00e1c Madridista. H\u1ecd xem Ronaldo nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng Raul Gonzalez, ng\u01b0\u1eddi trao l\u1ea1i \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i cho anh. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u00f9ng b\u1ed9 s\u1eadu c\u0169ng v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m K\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t Mourinho khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m K\u1ebb hai m\u1eb7t Mourinho khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Quan-diem-Ke-hai-mat-Mourinho-khien-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1eeb Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c cho Ronaldo ghi trung b\u00ecnh 50 b\u00e0n/ m\u00f9a, m\u1eb7c anh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 t\u00f4n s\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. Ch\u00ednh tri\u1ebft l\u00fd tr\u1ecdng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Real tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n nh\u1edb v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 4 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, khi Real \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Juventus t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i Champions League, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb c\u00fa &ldquo;ng\u1ea3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e8n&rdquo; n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. <u>\u0110\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Allianz b\u1eadt c\u1ea3 d\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ed7 tay t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3</u> b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p anh \u0111ang hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juve.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ronaldo \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3m k\u00edch v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00eam h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3</strong>. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e2n Allianz s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p huy ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ghi ban truoc Juventus\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo ghi ban truoc Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/4/Buffon-va-Max-Allegri-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Real-Madrid-vs-Juventus--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Ronaldo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh C\u0110V&nbsp;Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>D\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi cho M.U v\u00e0 Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>C\u0110V Juventus tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m l\u1edbn cho Ronaldo</em>, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 si\u00eau sao sinh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea3o Madeira \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB c\u0169 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n, h\u1eb3n gi\u1edd n\u00e0y Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Manchester thay v\u00ec Turin. 9 n\u0103m sau khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i, s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u1eabn h\u00e1t vang t\u00ean anh. <strong>C\u00e1c Manucians v\u1eabn xem anh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a CLB</strong>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Voi 6 nam so huu Ronaldo, Man Utd thu ve 3 trieu euro trong ban hop dong 100 trieu euro giua Real Madrid voi Juventus.\" title=\"V\u1edbi 6 n\u0103m s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo, Man Utd thu v\u1ec1 3 tri\u1ec7u euro trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u euro gi\u1eefa Real Madrid v\u1edbi Juventus.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c Manucians v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U m\u00e0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a Ronaldo v\u1ec1 l\u1ea1i ch\u1ed1n x\u01b0a. Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean b\u00e1o ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u0103n c\u1ee9. Su\u1ed1t 5 n\u0103m qua, c\u1ee5m t\u1eeb &ldquo;Ronaldo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U&rdquo; v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 hot.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1eady l\u00fd g\u00ec M.U kh\u00f4ng nghi\u00eam t\u00fac theo \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo h\u00e8 n\u00e0y? Juventus r\u1ea5t b\u1ea1o tay chi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro (99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) c\u00f9ng kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ m\u00f9a \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n n\u1eb1m trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi tr\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"lanh dao M.U Woodward va Mourinho\" title=\"lanh dao M.U Woodward va Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/lanh-dao-M.U-Woodward-va-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U mua Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu CLB gi\u00e0u nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kham n\u1ed5i, c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng ai &ldquo;gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u&rdquo; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo kh\u1ecfi Real. M\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 m\u00e0 Juventus d\u00e0nh cho Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec M.U \u0111ang tr\u1ea3 cho Alexis Sanchez (trong khi hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1m t\u00e0ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Ronaldo n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4i, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng mong \u0111\u1ee3i Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3n m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau khi c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb Real v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng <u>M.U khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo</u>. H\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Romelu Lukaku t\u1eeb Everton trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez t\u1eeb Arsenal trong m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ebfn h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ph\u00eda M.U hay m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus-176-190940.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m&rdquo; Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, th\u00f4ng tin Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7 m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Man...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Ronaldo trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Jose Mourinho \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Lukaku s\u1eafm vai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o duy nh\u1ea5t trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha r\u1ed3i Sanchez, Martial, Rashford, Lingard hay Mata thay nhau h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 xung quanh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn M.U ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Lukaku bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o vai Karim Benzema, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho ng\u00f4i sao 33 tu\u1ed5i trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Real. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i World Cup, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c nhau thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 trung phong c\u1eafm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku Bi vs Tunisia\" title=\"Lukaku B\u1ec9 vs Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/nguoi-anh-thach-thuc-ngoi-no-lukaku-trong-tran-chien-voi-bi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Lukaku c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1eafm nhi\u1ec1u vai tr\u00f2 kh\u00e1c nhau</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fd do x\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 <strong>Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 can thi\u1ec7p khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</strong>. &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t&rdquo; mu\u1ed1n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 trong kh\u00e2u chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 Mou s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o. Anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 ADN chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Real chinh ph\u1ee5c 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League sau 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. C\u00e1c m\u0169i c\u00f4ng Lukaku, Martial, Lingard hay Rashford&hellip; c\u1ee7a M.U ho\u1eb7c ch\u01b0a tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, ho\u1eb7c c\u00f2n non n\u1edbt trong khi Sanchez kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi t\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Mourinho\" title=\"Ronaldo va Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/quan-diem-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-va-su-ngan-can-cua-mourinho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf qua th\u00f9 x\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Real, <strong>Mourinho t\u1eebng c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Ronaldo</strong> \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean c\u1ea1nh kh\u00f3e \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o &ldquo;Mourinho \u0111\u1eebng nh\u1ed5 v\u00e0o c\u00e1i \u0111\u0129a m\u1edbi \u0103n xong&rdquo;, Ronaldo v\u00ec t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf qua chuy\u1ec7n c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu M.U ng\u1ecf l\u1eddi d\u00f9 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i hay n\u0103m nay, tin ch\u1eafc Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u00e0 d\u00f9 C\u0110V v\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00f3i c\u00f3, Mourinho v\u1eabn n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng. M\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, <em>\u00f4ng c\u00f2n gi\u1eef m\u1ed1i h\u1eadn x\u01b0a</em>. M\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 quy t\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n: <u>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong \u0111\u1ed9i</u>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd ph\u00fat n\u00e0y, Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. Cu\u1ed9c t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 M.U c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd x\u1ea3y ra v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 Mourinho m\u1edbi bi\u1ebft l\u00fd do n\u1eb1m \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/marotta-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-cach-chieu-mo-176-190965.html\">S\u1ebfp Juventus ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/infographics/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi-406-190961.html\">Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus-180-190910.html\">&ldquo;Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHo\u00e0i Dung (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1167","checkdouble":"191022"},{"date":"11:36 12/07","title":"Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u201cnh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 M\u201d, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 2 CLB th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/12/ivan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Man United, Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i, trong khi Tottenham nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi 8 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 2 CLB c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1982 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd.\r\n</h2><h2>Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra, Real Madrid l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018, trong khi Barcelona l\u00e0 CLB r\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 8 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Premier League \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 M.U, Man City, Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham g\u00f3p t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 29 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u1ede \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00ecn Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Inter Milan trong ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern v\u00e0 Inter l\u00e0 2 CLB c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018\" title=\"Tolisso v\u00e0 Perisic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/37045812_945004362354346_7684761511289421824_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern v\u00e0 Inter l\u00e0 2&nbsp;CLB c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. \u1ea2nh: Tr\u00ean \u0110\u01b0\u1eddng Pitch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, t\u00ednh t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup 1982 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Bayern v\u00e0 Inter Milan. Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt t\u1eebng l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch nh\u01b0 Ronaldo (Inter &ndash; 2002) hay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c (Bayern Munich &ndash; 2014).</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi &ldquo;quy lu\u1eadt&rdquo;, \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga &ndash; \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c